{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Castles Starter Pack</strong>\u202fincludes all of the features of the base game\u202f\u00a0<strong>PLUS 20 additional castle-themed assets</strong>\u202f perfect for creating a mighty fortress, an abandoned keep, or castle ruins.\u202f<strong>The DLC pack represents a tremendous value compared to purchasing assets separately with in-app purchases</strong>. The pack includes:\u00a0</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The base game for TTRPGs in 3D and Augmented Reality, and the Free Starter Set</strong>\u202f featuring digital dungeon and cavern terrain from Dwarven Forge and Fat Dragon Games, player minis from Hero Forge and Reaper Mini, plus our digital dice.\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3 x Ready-to-Play Maps</strong>:\u00a0 Lead the party in investigating a sunken and ruined keep, rumored to be haunted.\u00a0 Explore a King\u2019s mighty castle. It is heavily defended; will you storm in or try stealth? Seek a lost map amidst crumbling towers but be sure to evade the shrieking goblins and their evil Drow master!\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>5 x NPCs for your castle crawling adventure: a Guard, an Animated Suit of Armor, King Tiberious Blackstrand, a Dark Elf Paladin and an Adult Red Dragon\u202f\u00a0</strong>ready to jealously guard its horde!\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Stone curved wall, wall with arrow slits, stone floor, and winding stone staircase </strong>with which to build a mighty keep or castle turrets.\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ruined outer wall and ruined curved wall </strong>\u202fto create a keep ruined by time, the elements, or a terrible siege. Beware!\u00a0 It has long since been abandoned and who knows what you will discover.\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Heavy stone outerwall</strong>\u00a0used to create the impenetrable outer walls of the castle.\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Corridor stone wall, corridor stone wall with torch, and stone interior wall </strong>perfect for building the labyrinth tunnels that run under the castle and the halls that run along the perimeter.\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Castle gate and portcullis</strong>\u00a0built to withstand even the most determined invaders.\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A water tile</strong>: just duplicate the tile and create a complete castle moat!\u00a0</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A tree: </strong>copy/paste<strong> </strong>to create the surrounding forest!\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Remember: whether you use the ready-to-play maps, or create your own maps, you can share them with your TTRPG party for free and share your creations with the community on the Mirrorscape HUB!\u00a0</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733251754","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373470/page.bg.jpg?t=1733251754","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373470/43485ac70c67a948b217042465c6c0808d0169d0/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733251754","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373470/43485ac70c67a948b217042465c6c0808d0169d0/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733251754","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id"